User stories
  -As a user, I want to be able to login/logout
  -As a user, I want to be able to join/create a group
  -As a user, I want to be able to post a message to the group
  -As a user, I want to be able to tag a post
  -As a user, I want to be able to delete my post
  -As a user, I want to be able to edit my post
  -As a user, I want to be able to see all posts with a specific tag
  -posts in a group are only visible to the group
  -posts can only be edited by the author of the post







  Stretch:
  -owner of group able to moderate... i.e. accept users, delete posts etc...
  -As a user, I want to be able to send a private message
    -As a user, I want to be able to comment on a post



